Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: Products.PFGSelectionStringField
Version: 0.9.0
Summary: Products.PFGSelectionStringField is a field type for Products.PloneFormGen.
Home-page: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/Products.PFGSelectionStringField
Author: Taito Horiuchi
Author-email: taito.horiuchi@gmail.com
License: GPL
Description: Introduction
        ============
        ``Products.PFGSelectionStringField`` adds selection field with string field next to it to ``PloneFormGen``.
        
        This is useful when you need some comment with the selected option.
        
        Tested with
        -----------
        * Plone-4.1b2 and Plone-3.3.5
        * Products.PloneFormGen-1.6.0
        
        Installation
        ============
        
        Use zc.buildout and the plone.recipe.zope2instance
        recipe to manage packages:
        
        * Add ``Products.PFGSelectionStringField`` to the list of eggs to install, e.g.::
        
            [buildout]
            eggs =
                Products.PFGSelectionStringField
        
        * Re-run buildout, e.g. with::
        
            ./bin/buildout
        
